1
00:00:53,600 --> 00:00:54,240
Jiang Yue,

2
00:00:54,799 --> 00:00:56,560
are you serious about

3
00:00:57,079 --> 00:00:58,240
this half-sister of yours?

4
00:01:33,040 --> 00:01:34,439
Look, a shell.

5
00:01:35,480 --> 00:01:37,159
Poor little thing.

6
00:01:40,400 --> 00:01:41,200
Why?

7
00:01:41,719 --> 00:01:44,319
Everyone else is in the water,

8
00:01:44,599 --> 00:01:46,040
but it's all alone here,

9
00:01:46,040 --> 00:01:47,120
so lonely.

10
00:01:47,519 --> 00:01:49,120
It's not poor at all.

11
00:01:50,519 --> 00:01:51,719
Everyone else is in the water,

12
00:01:51,959 --> 00:01:52,959
only it is on the shore.

13
00:01:53,920 --> 00:01:56,799
And there is a super photographer

14
00:01:56,799 --> 00:01:57,879
taking its ID photo.

15
00:01:59,480 --> 00:02:00,560
You're so good.

16
00:02:41,319 --> 00:02:41,960
Lu Qi.

17
00:02:42,159 --> 00:02:43,120
Professor Chu.

18
00:02:43,120 --> 00:02:44,199
Look, Professor Chu.

19
00:02:44,439 --> 00:02:45,360
Why are you here?

20
00:02:49,159 --> 00:02:49,759
What a coincidence.

21
00:02:50,080 --> 00:02:51,639
I'm here to fish.

22
00:02:52,439 --> 00:02:53,680
You can fish?

23
00:02:54,319 --> 00:02:55,520
But I'm not lucky today.

24
00:02:56,319 --> 00:02:57,199
You two have fun.

25
00:02:57,479 --> 00:02:58,199
I'll try somewhere else.

26
00:02:58,879 --> 00:02:59,560
Professor Chu

27
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:00,879
Well

28
00:03:01,199 --> 00:03:03,439
I'm going to take part in the photography contest of ENT.

29
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:05,840
Have you prepared your work?

30
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:09,680
I haven't got any idea yet.

31
00:03:11,120 --> 00:03:12,439
It will be due in a week.

32
00:03:12,919 --> 00:03:13,879
You need to hurry up.

33
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:16,840
So I want to ask you for advice.

34
00:03:17,840 --> 00:03:19,039
If you have time.

35
00:03:23,159 --> 00:03:23,840
Of course.

36
00:03:25,439 --> 00:03:26,199
She doesn't have time.

37
00:03:31,319 --> 00:03:32,759
Your brother is still worried about you.

38
00:03:33,159 --> 00:03:34,080
Maybe next time.

39
00:03:35,159 --> 00:03:35,840
Professor Chu

40
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:38,879
There is only one week left.

41
00:03:39,039 --> 00:03:39,520
I'm afraid...

42
00:03:39,759 --> 00:03:40,240
It's okay.

43
00:03:41,599 --> 00:03:42,840
I have a house nearby.

44
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:43,879
It's at 13 on the beach.

45
00:03:44,240 --> 00:03:44,800
You can come.

46
00:03:44,800 --> 00:03:45,199
Lu Qi.

47
00:03:47,919 --> 00:03:48,599
Jiang Yue.

48
00:03:50,240 --> 00:03:50,919
Building 6, No. 13.

49
00:03:51,520 --> 00:03:52,199
I'm here every weekend.

50
00:03:52,719 --> 00:03:53,240
I can wait for you.

51
00:03:55,319 --> 00:03:56,120
Professor Chu.

52
00:03:56,840 --> 00:03:57,360
Well.

53
00:03:57,800 --> 00:04:00,120
I won't disturb your rest.

54
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:02,800
Maybe next time

55
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:03,960
when you have time,

56
00:04:04,520 --> 00:04:05,639
I'll ask you for advice.

57
00:04:05,919 --> 00:04:06,800
Thank you, Professor Chu.

58
00:04:09,639 --> 00:04:10,039
Alright.

59
00:04:18,040 --> 00:04:18,680
Mr. Jiang,

60
00:04:19,720 --> 00:04:20,920
there's something I don't understand.

61
00:04:21,959 --> 00:04:23,360
Why are you so hostile to me?

62
00:04:24,399 --> 00:04:25,319
You know it very well.

63
00:04:38,800 --> 00:04:39,800
It's going to be a heavy rain outside.

64
00:04:40,199 --> 00:04:40,920
It's not safe to walk at night.

65
00:04:42,680 --> 00:04:43,839
Could you please help me book two rooms?

66
00:04:44,399 --> 00:04:45,600
One moment, please.

67
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:47,720
I'm sorry, sir.

68
00:04:47,959 --> 00:04:48,639
There's only one room left.

69
00:04:49,680 --> 00:04:50,079
Let's go.

70
00:04:50,600 --> 00:04:51,240
Your ID, please.

71
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:04,959
Okay.

72
00:05:05,040 --> 00:05:05,439
One moment, please.

73
00:05:07,959 --> 00:05:08,600
Here's your room card.

74
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:14,959
Let's go.

75
00:05:19,959 --> 00:05:20,360
Auntie,

76
00:05:21,199 --> 00:05:22,519
I'm taking Qi out for a walk.

77
00:05:23,759 --> 00:05:24,480
She didn't make a fuss.

78
00:05:25,240 --> 00:05:26,079
We'll be back tomorrow.

79
00:05:26,639 --> 00:05:27,399
You should get some rest.

80
00:05:38,759 --> 00:05:39,519
You go to bed.

81
00:05:40,519 --> 00:05:41,240
What about you?

82
00:05:41,879 --> 00:05:42,519
The sofa.

83
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:44,120
Okay.

84
00:05:45,240 --> 00:05:45,800
Good night.

85
00:05:46,120 --> 00:05:46,600
Good night.

86
00:05:49,639 --> 00:05:50,199
Jiang Yue,

87
00:05:51,279 --> 00:05:52,439
I want to talk to you.

88
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:56,279
First,

89
00:05:56,959 --> 00:05:59,160
thank you for taking me out today.

90
00:05:59,839 --> 00:06:00,519
You're welcome.

91
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:02,879
I want to know

92
00:06:03,800 --> 00:06:05,639
why you don't like Chu Mo.

93
00:06:06,399 --> 00:06:07,560
He's not an ordinary painter.

94
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:11,920
He has a lot of life stages

95
00:06:11,920 --> 00:06:12,920
that are deliberately left blank.

96
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:16,879
It seems to have been deliberately erased by someone.

97
00:06:18,920 --> 00:06:19,920
You had someone investigate him?

98
00:06:20,839 --> 00:06:21,920
Our family has a special identity.

99
00:06:23,439 --> 00:06:24,720
There are many malicious business wars

100
00:06:24,839 --> 00:06:26,240
that are crueler than you can imagine.

101
00:06:27,600 --> 00:06:28,920
I don't want you to get involved in it.

102
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:33,839
Jiang Yue,

103
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:36,279
I'm not interested in your family's

104
00:06:36,279 --> 00:06:36,959
business.

105
00:06:37,959 --> 00:06:39,759
Maybe just as you guessed,

106
00:06:40,519 --> 00:06:43,040
Mr. Chu Mo has

107
00:06:43,959 --> 00:06:45,399
his own purpose.

108
00:06:46,519 --> 00:06:47,759
But for me,

109
00:06:49,600 --> 00:06:50,759
I can learn a lot

110
00:06:50,959 --> 00:06:52,240
from him.

111
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:54,439
Do what you want to do.

112
00:06:56,399 --> 00:06:57,399
Leave the rest to me.

113
00:06:59,839 --> 00:07:00,439
Go to sleep.

114
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:06,160
Jiang Yue,

115
00:07:07,560 --> 00:07:08,759
tell me about yourself.

116
00:07:11,519 --> 00:07:12,759
What do you want to do in the future?

117
00:07:13,920 --> 00:07:14,920
Listen to my father.

118
00:07:15,920 --> 00:07:18,879
Why should your father decide what you do?

119
00:07:22,639 --> 00:07:23,680
My mother

120
00:07:24,800 --> 00:07:26,160
died in a fire.

121
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:28,759
I just want to find out the truth

122
00:07:29,199 --> 00:07:30,199
and avenge her.

123
00:07:33,399 --> 00:07:34,560
I'll do whatever

124
00:07:35,959 --> 00:07:36,839
my father tells me to do.

125
00:07:37,920 --> 00:07:39,519
I'll do anything

126
00:07:41,439 --> 00:07:42,480
to avenge my mother.

127
00:07:42,920 --> 00:07:44,120
Who killed my mother?

128
00:07:44,360 --> 00:07:45,199
I want revenge.

129
00:07:45,759 --> 00:07:46,759
From now on,

130
00:07:48,240 --> 00:07:49,279
you have to listen to me.

131
00:08:01,199 --> 00:08:02,839
Dad, I'm in pain.

132
00:08:04,079 --> 00:08:06,199
Did you forget how your mother died?

133
00:08:46,799 --> 00:08:48,320
[I never thought]

134
00:08:48,840 --> 00:08:50,919
[his world would be so cold.]

135
00:08:51,639 --> 00:08:53,159
[The warmth he gave me,]

136
00:08:54,039 --> 00:08:56,200
[was it also something he never had in his life?]

137
00:09:05,399 --> 00:09:06,399
We've lost District D.

138
00:09:06,720 --> 00:09:07,960
We have to find a way to make up for it.

139
00:09:08,840 --> 00:09:10,320
Otherwise, we won't pass the test from the higher-ups.

140
00:09:17,320 --> 00:09:18,759
Let Jiang Yue send a Make Your Bones

141
00:09:19,039 --> 00:09:19,879
to District 45.

142
00:09:20,399 --> 00:09:21,039
District 45?

143
00:09:21,960 --> 00:09:22,399
Sir,

144
00:09:22,919 --> 00:09:24,120
you said...

145
00:09:24,759 --> 00:09:25,679
Only if he goes

146
00:09:25,679 --> 00:09:27,200
can it represent our sincerity.

147
00:09:29,840 --> 00:09:30,279
Forget it.

148
00:09:30,679 --> 00:09:31,399
I'll tell him.

149
00:09:31,720 --> 00:09:32,240
You go ahead.

150
00:09:36,559 --> 00:09:37,360
Changfa,

151
00:09:38,039 --> 00:09:38,840
Qi Qi...

152
00:09:41,840 --> 00:09:42,480
She's grown up.

153
00:09:43,120 --> 00:09:44,519
It's good to have her own opinion.

154
00:09:45,159 --> 00:09:46,039
Is Jiang Yue home?

155
00:09:46,480 --> 00:09:47,360
He's not.

156
00:09:59,039 --> 00:09:59,919
Let me take you to school.

157
00:10:01,000 --> 00:10:01,840
I don't have classes today.

158
00:10:02,200 --> 00:10:03,159
Let's go home.

159
00:10:04,639 --> 00:10:04,879
Okay.

160
00:10:11,879 --> 00:10:12,600
Be careful.

161
00:10:12,840 --> 00:10:13,559
I'm fine.

162
00:10:13,559 --> 00:10:14,240
You're back.

163
00:10:16,240 --> 00:10:17,080
Haven't eaten yet, right?

164
00:10:17,320 --> 00:10:17,919
What do you want to eat?

165
00:10:17,919 --> 00:10:18,879
Let the aunt go shopping.

166
00:10:19,360 --> 00:10:19,879
Anything is fine.

167
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:20,919
What about you?

168
00:10:21,559 --> 00:10:22,120
Anything is fine for me too.

169
00:10:32,919 --> 00:10:33,960
I'll go find my father.

170
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:46,000
Father.

171
00:10:49,200 --> 00:10:51,039
Remember to report when you go on a long trip.

172
00:10:53,000 --> 00:10:54,399
Send this to the designated location.

173
00:11:03,039 --> 00:11:04,000
What's inside?

174
00:11:04,759 --> 00:11:06,440
It's a list of clients.

175
00:11:08,039 --> 00:11:09,200
The group has been tricked.

176
00:11:09,200 --> 00:11:10,000
The loss is huge.

177
00:11:12,720 --> 00:11:14,840
Only by sharing this list can we protect ourselves.

178
00:11:16,159 --> 00:11:16,639
And

179
00:11:18,600 --> 00:11:21,120
if that butterfly you mentioned shows up again,

180
00:11:21,240 --> 00:11:22,799
just crush him for me.

181
00:11:24,600 --> 00:11:26,399
I don't want to hear of any accidents.

182
00:11:27,799 --> 00:11:28,240
Understood.
